==============================================================================
ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
==============================================================================
PORT: The port the Express server will listen on.
EXPECTED: Integer (e.g., 3000, 8080)
PORT=3000
GITHUB_PAT: (Optional) Personal Access Token to bypass the 60 req/hr unauthenticated limit.
EXPECTED: String (GitHub token starting with ghp_ or github_pat_)
GITHUB_PAT=
ALLOWED_ORIGINS: (Optional) Comma-separated list of allowed origins for CORS.
EXPECTED: (String e.g., "https://wwww.{your-site}.com", "http://localhost:5173")
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=*
